page.title: 20GARDEN CENTRE SALES,W'BOLD
page.content:
In {Wychbold}we have {Webb's Garden {Centre}and the packets of seeds are well known all over the country.On a visit to the centre we found that it was not the seeds that were best sellers,so we asked for information about the types of sale.The graph of {sales}was as follows:
{********}Trees and shrubs {*******}Sundries {******}House plants {*****}Compost {****}Flowers and seeds {***}Fencing and slabs {**}Furniture and aquatics {*}Fruit trees,vegetables,books and jam
The company propogates 3/4 of all the plants and shrubs sold in the main area and in 1984 its total turn-over exceeded one million pounds.
